original_title: Rombongan Cik Kiah Ke Sukan Komanwel
overview: This drama tells the story of a group of villagers who visit the opening ceremony of the Commonwealth Games led by Cik Kiah. Various incidents and obstacles faced them before and during the journey to Bukit Jalil. The variety of hassles, differences and complaints from each participant of the group due to the late arrival of the bus and the poor condition of the bus made Cik Kiah have to be patient and calm them down. Enjoy watching this comedy drama full of values ​​and patriotism.
title: Rombongan Cik Kiah Ke Sukan Komanwel
